{
  "stem": "7069.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's the first time how we heard each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How we were able to hearing each other, I mean, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so then soon after that, my wife and I snuck out over the-- over the Russian-controlled borders.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very dangerous thing at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Russians were very, very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they would catch you out of your premises, too, they would nail you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we went to Munich to visit my brother and his wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, how we happened to meet?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My wife and I, we knew each other from before, because her mother was friends with the parents of a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so during these sessions that I told you, when we were always together with youth groups, even the adults would meet each other like as the Germans say, they call a coffee klatch.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would meet there and the women would talk, and the men would play card games or something like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would sit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you couldn't go anyplace, as I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Remember that.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we, the young-- our young group, the musicians group, we met and went into another room and had our fun there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now my wife, Inge, was-- and I'm talking at the time when I was 17 years old. 16, 17, 18-year-old during that time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And since she's a few years older, she didn't look much like a-- a woman to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She looked to me at the time like a little girl who was the daughter of one of our mutual friends.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so I didn't pay too much attention to her, I must admit, at the time I went through.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
